title: Zeityear 10/27: 'Lightyear', Shiba Inu Coin, 'Tiger King 2', NYPD, Drew Barrymore, Frederic Arnault

description:
In this edition of Zeityear, Jack and Miles discuss the trailer for the film 'Lightyear', Shiba Inu Coin to going to the moon, the 'Tiger King 2' trailer, the NYPD vaccine mandate, the Drew Barrymore/Tom Green reunion, and Frederic Arnault being the third richest rich guy
